  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_4_5100-5186",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5100-5186",
      "markText": "就像一个勤快的笨蛋总是要比一般的笨蛋干出更多不可收拾的蠢事一样，一个自以为是而又事必躬亲的专制君主给这个千疮百孔的帝国造成的伤害，远远要大过一个平庸、惰怠、无所事事的皇帝。",
      "totalCount": 285,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5100&rangeEnd=5186",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5100&rangeEnd=5186"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_2_108-154",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "108-154",
      "markText": "当地一户农民院子里的一株李子树，结出的果实不是往年那种圆而翠的李子，而是八竿子打不着的黄瓜。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=108&rangeEnd=154",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=108&rangeEnd=154"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_2_5826-5855",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "5826-5855",
      "markText": "他的性格决定了他将和祖宗打下的江山一起走向万劫不复的深渊。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=5826&rangeEnd=5855",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=5826&rangeEnd=5855"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_2_421-466",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "421-466",
      "markText": "与此相类，王朝更替，社会大动荡即将到来之时，底层民众往往多了些敏感，而达官贵人却浑然不觉。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=421&rangeEnd=466",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=421&rangeEnd=466"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_4_2589-2662",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2589-2662",
      "markText": "后来李自成攻占北京，从明宫搜出的白银竟多达三千七百多万两，黄金和其他珠宝还不在内。为了节省一百万而丢掉三千七百万乃至无法估价的整座江山，是否值得？",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2589&rangeEnd=2662",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2589&rangeEnd=2662"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_5_6797-6883",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6797-6883",
      "markText": "加派剿饷和练饷是为了筹集足够多的费用来平定民变，然而费用的筹集过程同时也是激发民变的过程。一方面在努力平息民变，一方面又在努力激发民变。这个奇怪的悖论，崇祯到死也没有搞懂。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6797&rangeEnd=6883",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6797&rangeEnd=6883"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_1_294-346",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "294-346",
      "markText": "对百姓来说，要么饿死，要么被杀，要么起而杀人；对官员来说，要么死于异族，要么死于农民军，要么被朝廷处死。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=294&rangeEnd=346",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=294&rangeEnd=346"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_2_509-537",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "509-537",
      "markText": "李子树长出黄瓜也许是基因的变异。但身处末世的人并不这么看",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=509&rangeEnd=537",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=509&rangeEnd=537"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_2_3462-3500",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "3462-3500",
      "markText": "也是至关重要的，李建泰明确表示不需要国家拨给军费，而是由自己出钱为国家打仗。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3462&rangeEnd=3500",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3462&rangeEnd=3500"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_11_5987-6036",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "5987-6036",
      "markText": "当然，至于后来清军入关所带来的血腥暴政，乃至于中国遭遇亘古未有之惨烈巨变，那是另一个层面上的问题。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5987&rangeEnd=6036",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5987&rangeEnd=6036"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_1_438-488",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "438-488",
      "markText": "这悲剧，不仅在于中国历史上最后一个汉族王朝走向了灭亡，更在于纯正的古典精神到此画上了一个永远的句号。",
      "totalCount": 132,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43385901&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=438&rangeEnd=488",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/263323d07296042d2633a6f?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=438&rangeEnd=488"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43385901_13_3641-3714",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3641-3714",
      "markText": "不可思议的是，尽管对清王朝起到了如此重要的作用，到了乾隆年间，当大清的统治日益稳固，洪承畴却被列入了深含贬意的《贰臣传》。这就是扑朔迷离的中国史。",
